== 資訊 ==
* Mew（Jonas Bjerre、Bo Madsen、Johan Wohlert、Silas Graae）—演唱、演奏

* Bo Rande—翼號（第2、3首）、小號（第13、14首）
* Lasse Mauritzen—法國號（第2、3、14首）
* Rebecca Stark—女高音（第2、8首）
* J. Mascis—演唱（第3、10首）
* Damon Tutunjian—吉他（第5首）
* Mathias Aagaard Christensen—合唱（第13首）
* Frederik Peter Jakobsen—合唱（第13首）
* Niklas Emil De Fries—合唱（第13首）
* Frederik Stadager Larsen—合唱（第13首）

== 其他 ==
* Pitchfork Media『'''Your Cover's Blown''': ''Pitchfork's ongoing guide to the worst in album art''』評選為最差專輯封面第二名[https://web.archive.org/web/20070312042812/http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/page/news/category/yourcoversblown]。
* Pitchfork Media『'''Top 25 Worst Album Covers Of 2006'''』評選為最差專輯封面之一[https://web.archive.org/web/20070106164338/http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/feature/40185/Staff_List_Top_25_Worst_Album_Covers_of_2006]。
{{cquote|''We thought it was a bit bold for a band of our type to put our faces on the cover," Mew's Jonas Bjerre told Pitchfork in October. A bit bold, indeed. What are you talking about! This is grotesque! (No, seriously, it's [http://www.ultimate-horror.com/slashers/grotesque.jpg Grotesque].) They couldn't just get some drawing of a coat like every other Danish band?''}}

